<HEADLINE> Jiang Zemin Stresses Unity (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
He said the report adopted by the congress has reviewed the
struggle of the Chinese nation over the past 100 years from a
historical perspective, and has looked into the future to make a
comprehensive plan for the cross-century development of China's
reform and modernization drive.
</P>
<P>
"It is our Party's political announcement and guiding document
in leading all Chinese people to forge ahead into the 21st
century," Jiang noted.
</P>
<P>
He went on to note that the other cross-century significance of
the congress lies in its election of a new CPC Central Committee
and the Committee's leading body -- the Political Bureau and its
Standing Committee.
</P>
<P>
"The results of this congress have won hearty support of all
Chinese people, and have been highly valued in the international
community as well," Jiang said.
</P>
<P>
Holding high the great banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory is the
soul of the congress, he said, and the issue of the banner is of
critical importance.
</P>
<P>
"This issue is vital to the consolidation and development of
the cause of building socialism with Chinese characteristics, and
is directly related to the fundamental interests of all Chinese
people," Jiang explained.
</P>
<P>
During the congress, he said, the Party has decided to write
explicitly in its Constitution that Deng Xiaoping Theory is its
guiding ideology and must be steadfastly followed.
</P>
<P>
"This not only has fully displayed our determination to advance
along the road of building socialism with Chinese characteristics
pioneered by Comrade Xiaoping, but also represented the common
aspirations of the people of various ethnic groups across the
country," he noted.
</P>
