U.S. officials said that Albright had worked very hard in an
effort to reopen the peace talks between Israelis and Palestinians.
</P>
<P>
An announcement is expected later this afternoon after the
three-party meeting.
</P>
<P>
The Palestinians sought to include in the statement a provision
strongly discouraging Israel's expansion of settlements on the
West Bank while Israel resists the inclusion, diplomatic sources
said. 
