<HEADLINE> Over 140 Delegations to Be in World Junior Games </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, September 30 (Xinhua) -- A total of 141 countries and
regions have confirmed to take part in next year's first World
Junior Games.
</P>
<P>
Organizers invited 183 nations and regions to the iniatial
World Junior Games held in Moscow in July next year, but only nine
have expressed their missing, the organizers said Friday.
</P>
<P>
Host Russia sends a 321-member delegation to compete in the 14
events at the Games. 
</P>
