with Patrick Cheng Yiu-chung, president of City University of Hong
Kong, and his 22-member group from the Hong Kong educational
circle today, who are here to attend the capital city's grand
National Day ceremony.
</P>
<P>
Education is the base on which to build up the nation and to
honor teachers and revere their work is a good Chinese tradition,
Li said.
</P>
<P>
He looked forward to further cooperation between Hong Kong and
interior educational circles.
</P>
<P>
