<HEADLINE> Beijing Reception Marks 48th National Day (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"We are convinced that under the guidance of Deng Xiaoping
Theory and the leadership of the Party Central Committee with
Comrade Jiang Zemin at the core, the Chinese people of all ethnic
groups, through hard work in united struggle, will certainly score
new achievements next year in reform and opening-up and the
socialist modernization drive," Li said.
</P>
<P>
Since the return of Hong Kong to the motherland, he noted, the
policies of "one country, two systems," "Hong Kong people
governing Hong Kong" and a high degree of autonomy have been
implemented and the Government of the Hong Kong Special
Administrative Region (SAR) has been performing well.
</P>
<P>
The recent annual meetings of the World Bank Group and the
International Monetary Fund, which were successfully held in Hong
Kong, have increased the international community's understanding
of Hong Kong and have shown that the status of Hong Kong as an
international financial center is highly valued and people are
confident in Hong Kong's long-term prosperity and stability, he
said.
</P>
<P>
Preparations for Macao's return to the motherland in 1999 are
progressing smoothly, the premier said.
</P>
<P>
"To resolve the Taiwan issue in accordance with the policy of
`peaceful reunification and one country, two systems' is our
principled position," he said, expressing the hope that Taiwan
authorities will set store by the overall national interests and
begin political negotiations with the mainland under the one-China
principle at an early date.
</P>
<P>
"No matter how many difficulties we might encounter on our road
of advance, the goal of complete national reunification will be
finally achieved," he said.
</P>
