<HEADLINE> Leaders of Vietnam, Laos Congratulate China on National Day </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 30 (Xinhua) -- Leaders of Vietnam and Laos
have sent congratulatory messages to Chinese leaders Jiang Zemin,
Li Peng and Qiao Shi on the celebration of China's 48th National
Day.
</P>
<P>
In their message, general secretary of the Communist Party of
Vietnam Nam Do Muoi and Vietnamese President Tram Duc Luong said,
"we are happy to see that the Chinese people have made great
progress and achievements in their continuous efforts to open-up
and reform, and by raising the people's living standards and
China's international status in the past year."
</P>
<P>
The successful 15th National Congress of the Communist Party of
China (CPC) is a milestone in advancing the socialist cause with
Chinese characteristics into the 21st century, they said.
</P>
<P>
Vietnam continues to attach importance to the friendship and
good neighborly relations with China on the basis of mutual
benefit, they noted.
</P>
<P>
They said they believed that cooperative relations between the
two countries will be strengthened and consolidated in the
interests of peace, stability and development in the region as
well as the world.
</P>
<P>
They said, "We sincerely hope the Chinese people, Guided by the
guidelines adopted by the CPC during its recently completed 15th
National Congress and under the leadership of the CPC, will make even
greater achievements in the course of building their country.
</P>
<P>
President of the Lao People's Revolutionary Party, Prime
Minister Khamtay Siphandone and President of State Nouhak
Phoumsavan said in their message that the Chinese people, by
persisting in their socialist path with Chinese characteristics,
have made marked achievements in their course of reform and
opening-up.
</P>
<P>
China's economy and the people's living standards have improved
steadily and its comprehensive national strength has been
reinforced, giving it greater social stability, they said.
</P>
<P>
They also said Hong Kong's return to China this year has
enhanced China's international reputation and credibility, and it
has also contributed to the reunification of China and to world
peace, stability and cooperation.
</P>
<P>
They expressed the wish that the brotherly Chinese people enjoy
more and greater achievements under the leadership of the CPC,
with Jiang Zemin at the core, by upholding the banner of Deng
Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics. 
</P>
