with 29 cases have been reported since January this year.
</P>
<P>
A number of people have been arrested and prosecuted in
connection with the murder, said the police commander.
</P>
<P>
The tragedies were resulted from high illiteracy rate coupled
with poor medical care service, according to Mwanza Regional
Commissioner James Luhanga. 
