<HEADLINE> Vice-Premier Meets Trinidad and Tobago Finance Minister </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 30 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Vice-Premier Zhu
Rongji met here today with Brian Kuei Tung, minister of Finance
