cooperation and forge closer bilateral economic and trade ties.
</P>
<P>
Zhu briefed Tung on China's reform, opening and economic
construction.
</P>
<P>
Tung said he will extend the greatest possible effort to
strengthen mutual understanding and cooperation, and raise
friendly bilateral ties to a new level.
</P>
<P>
Tung is visiting China as guest of Chinese Finance Minister
Liu Zhongli.
</P>
<P>
Chinese Vice-Minister of Finance Liu Jibin also attended the
meeting. 
</P>
</TEXT>
